import React from 'react'
import { Button } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import './styles.scss';

const ContactUsButton = () => (

    <Button
        size='huge'
        color="green"
        className='ds-contact-us-button display-desktop-only to-phone'
    >
        <Icon name="download" />
        Download
</Button>
)

export default ContactUsButton;
